The application runs on the corporate intranet only (not accessible from the public internet). Content Security Policy headers are configured with `script-src 'self'`. The backend does not maintain a token blacklist — JWTs are validated only by signature and expiration. There is no refresh token mechanism — users must re-authenticate after 24 hours.

